#### Media settings
## volume control
bindsym XF86AudioMute exec "ponymix toggle"
bindsym XF86AudioLowerVolume exec "ponymix decrease 5; ponymix unmute"
bindsym XF86AudioRaiseVolume exec "ponymix increase 5; ponymix unmute"

